# Groonga package

Target: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Components:

- xxHash @XXHASH_VERSION@
- msgpack-c @MSGPACKC_VERSION@
- Groonga @GROONGA_VERSION@

This prefix is intended to be consumed by PGroonga builds. It provides
Groonga headers, libraries, pkg-config metadata, and CMake package metadata.
